Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.34,0:00:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,指定幸存者  前情提要\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Previously on Designated Survivor...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经被英国大使馆全职录用了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I've been posted full-time with the British embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,立即生效\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Effective immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾去圣卢西亚度假吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Did you take a vacation on St. Lucia?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我和女儿每年都一起旅行一次\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Every year, my daughter and I take one trip together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,今年去圣卢西亚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}This year, St. Lucia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你被弗斯特传唤了吗  因为什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You're being subpoenaed by Foerstel? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.19,0:00:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他发现了一个在圣卢西亚由埃里克·利特尔注册的银行账户\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He's found a St. Lucian bank account set up by Eric Little,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,六个月前  以我的名义\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}six months ago, in my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我被陷害了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I'm being set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.03,0:00:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,利特尔被谋杀的事件调查怎么样了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Where are we with Little's murder investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.78,0:00:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,此时没有任何进展  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Nothing on that front, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你能把利特尔和劳埃德联系起来么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Were you able to tie Little to Lloyd?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.79,0:00:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没有证据能够把他俩连在一起\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}There's no evidence that connects them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你是切片面包出现以来最棒的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You're the greatest thing since sliced bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.58,0:00:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,面包很棒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And bread is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,基础性的棒  就像是水  空气  还有你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Fundamentally great. Like water. Or air. Or you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.71,0:00:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有问题吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.13,0:00:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,从车上下来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Step out of the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,指控已经被撤了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}The charges were dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的职责是让总统知道并没有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}But my duty to inform the president wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.35,0:00:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,收了一大箱信件吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}? Got a box full of letters ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你也许会愿意读读\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}? Think you might like to read ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这也许是你想看看的东西  但收信人写的全都是我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}? Some things that you might like to see But they're all addressed to me ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,期待我有很多答复吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}? Wish I had a lotta answers ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.74,0:01:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因为本应该那样\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}? 'Cause that's the way it should be ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.79,0:01:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,对于所有直接给我的问题\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}? For all these questions Being directed at me ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,三信日吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Three-letter day?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.59,0:01:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,每个月  白宫都能收到超过10，000封信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Every month, the White House receives 10,000 letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,总统会选三封进行回复\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}The president chooses three letters to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.22,0:01:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们应该怎么做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}How does that involve us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们调查请求并建议总统\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}We investigate the requests and advise the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那可真刺激  - 是哦\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- That's exciting. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.26,0:01:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,三信日可以看作红色信件日\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Three-letter day can be a red-letter day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我才不干呢  - 我也是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- I'm not doing this. - For some.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢信件  我不爱读也不爱写\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I don't like letters. I don't read or write them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是哪个混蛋的主意  - 总统的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Whose asinine idea was this? - The president's.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我加入  - 好样的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- I'm in. - Attaboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.44,0:01:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 三信日  朋友  - 噢  给我一枪吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Three-letter day,amigo. - Oh, somebody please shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嗨\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Hey. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.03,0:01:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不仅仅是象征性的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Today is not just simply symbolic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在今天  我们将真正为选民服务\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Today, we are gonna truly serve the electorate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,通过努力回答他们的具体要问题\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}by trying to answer their specific requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.83,0:01:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,亚伦和艾米莉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Aaron and Emily,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:02:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这封信是由上士丹尼尔·戈夫的寡妇写的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}this was written by the widow of Daniel Goff, Sergeant First Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,她问为什么她的丈夫被拒绝授予荣誉勋章\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}She asks why her husband was denied the Medal of Honor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.09,0:02:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,为了他在自由与坚毅行动中的勇敢和最终牺牲\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}for his ultimate sacrifice and bravery during Operation Enduring Freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在调查  - 没问题\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- On it. - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,赛斯和里奥\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Seth and Lyor,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,帮助亚当森先生找出什么杀死了他的蜜蜂\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}help Mr. Adamson figure out what's killing his bees.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 蜜蜂吗  - 是的  蜜蜂\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Bees? - Yes, bees.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,它们是指示物种\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}They are an indicator species.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,它们为我们80％的作物授粉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}They pollinate over 80% of our crops.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,它们死了  植物就会死  人类也不久就会死\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}They die, plants die, man will shortly follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,尽我们所能去了解什么是杀害他的蜜蜂是符合我们利益的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It's in our interest to do what we can to find out what's killing his bees.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢你  这是一个无上荣光  - 我确定你会做得很好的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Thank you. This is a solemn honor. - I'm sure you'll do great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 头奖  - 蛇眼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Jackpot! - Snake eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,肯德拉  这是一个在联邦死刑案件的赦免请求\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Kendra, this is a request for a pardon in a federal death penalty case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,自2003以来没有联邦执行赦免\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}There hasn't been a federal execution since 2003.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他定于本星期五死于注射死刑\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He's scheduled to die by lethal injection this Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一封来自佛罗里达州温特黑文的匿名信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}An anonymous letter from Winter Haven, Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,为了钱德勒·德恩寻求赦免机会吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Seeking clemency for Chandler Dern?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他是一名药剂师  罪名是他在2001杀死了一名缉毒人员\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He was a pharmacist convicted of killing a DEA agent in 2001.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,写这封信的人说  德恩不服他的判决但这个人不是这样想的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}This writer says that Dern appealed his sentence, but not his conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是吸引人  很奇怪  对吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}That's what caught my eye. Strange, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,闻所未闻  考虑到利害关系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Unheard of, given the stakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想把我的判断强加给陪审团\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I'm not inclined to impose my judgment over a jury's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你发现任何东西来证明判决的不公\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}But if you found anything to indicate manifest injustice,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我愿意了解  - 我会调查的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- I would wanna know. - I'll get cracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你有72小时\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You got 72 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,明白  先生  我们还有一件事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Understood. Sir, we have another issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你妻子的传票有了新进展  我们应该谈谈\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}There's been a development in regards to your wife's subpoena. We should talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,弗斯特愿意不公开程序吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Foerstel's offering to seal the proceedings?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个前提\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}With one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是你不会取消传票\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}That you don't move to quash your subpoena.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这是个交易  用保密交换合作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}So an inducement. Secrecy in exchange for cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果亚历克斯出现了并且她的证词会引起刑事诉讼  这样就会公开了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}If Alex appears and her answers lead to an indictment, that will go public.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这是可预见的风险\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It's a calculated risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你把这件事解决的几率有多大\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}What are the odds that you can get this tossed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,抛硬币几率吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It's a coin flip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你的情况这样的事情是十分特殊的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}The case against you is wildly circumstantial.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,除非在圣卢西亚你名下的账户\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}With one exception. The account in St. Lucia in your name
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,由埃里克·利特尔开户的已经被毁了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}that Eric Little opened is damning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,除非汉娜·韦尔斯可以找到那个开户的银行职员\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Unless Hannah Wells can find the banker who set it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不能证明你清白\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}we cannot clear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,只有银行职员能够证明\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Only the banker can prove
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,第一夫人的圣卢西亚帐户是一个劳埃德陷阱\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}that the First Lady's St. Lucia account is a Lloyd set-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们永远不会透露那个名字  - 等着看吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- They'll never give you his name. - We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以是很有说服力的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I can be very persuasive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  我是斯隆小姐  来这见布鲁尔先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Hello, I'm Ms. Sloane. I'm here to see Mr. Brewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你想在圣卢西亚开户吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You'd like to open an account in St. Lucia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 代表他人  - 是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- On someone's behalf? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我们不提供的三方服务\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}That is a third-party service we do not offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我从一位可信任的朋友那里得知\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I have it from a trusted friend
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有一位职员提供这种服务\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}that one of your officers does offer the service.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意帮我和对的人连上线\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}If you could put me in touch with the right person,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我很乐意付你一笔额外费用\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I'd be happy to pay a premium.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我们不能帮助你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Sorry, but we are unable to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能告诉我这位职员的名字\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}If you could give me the name of the officer--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就到这里吧  日安\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}That will be all. Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道怎么玩枪就不要玩\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Don't play with guns if you don't know how to use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我  知道如何玩枪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Me, I know how to use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意给我那位职员的名字吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Would you like to give me the name of that bank officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,撤销是要看法官的决定\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Quashing this will come down to the judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  给第一夫人一个通行证\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yes. And the optics of giving the First Lady a pass
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对他们来说可能是举足轻重的事情\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}could weigh heavily on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对他们来说举足轻重的事情  是这件事真的是陷害\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}What should weigh heavily on them is that this is a set-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 亚历克斯  - 我们决定撤销  汤姆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Alex. - We're moving to quash, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你能给我们几分钟吗  我们得谈谈这事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Could you give us a moment? We need to discuss this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的  先生  - 谢谢你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Yes, sir. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这场迫害已经持续几个月了  - 我知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- This witch hunt has lasted months. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想给弗斯特任何喘息的机会\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I don't want to give Foerstel any more oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们利用它能利用的一切  每一个程序性的策略和战略\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Every procedural maneuver, stratagem, we'll avail ourselves of all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只是在推迟不可避免的事情\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}That's only putting off the inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,弗斯特不会退缩\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Foerstel won't back down
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你引用的联邦议事规则\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}because you quote the  Federal Rules of Procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是我们唯一可行的策略  - 这是我们迄今为止所做的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- It's our only viable tactic. - It's what we've been doing so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,打防守  然后看看我们才到哪一步\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Playing defense, and look where it's gotten us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 更靠近悬崖  - 那我们就退后一步\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Closer to the precipice. - Then let's step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,亚历克斯  你是位勇士\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Alex, you are a fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我爱你众多理由中的一个\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It's one of the many things I love about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们不是在对抗这件事  而是在躲藏\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}But we're not fighting this, we're hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,假装这事儿就会这样过去  但它不会\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Pretending like it'll blow over. It won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:06:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这场暴风雨已经袭击我们有一阵了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}This storm has been coming at us for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们试着反转它  但没成功\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}We tried to outrun it, but we couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们采取不同的策略  深挖这件事  勇于直面这件事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}So we take a different tact, we dig in. We fight this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我今早翻身醒来你却不在了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I roll over this morning and you're not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那样可会让我感到不安  - 你需要睡美容觉嘛\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- That can give a guy a complex. - You needed your beauty sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能帮你追踪银行职员\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I could've helped you track down the banker
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那个帮着陷害第一夫人的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}who helped frame the First Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是两个人的活\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It wasn't a two-man job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你  汉娜·韦尔斯  是一匹独狼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You, Hannah Wells, are alone wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,追踪银行职员的名字\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Who hunted down the banker's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,说得对\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Touché.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的流氓银行家有什么消息\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Anything on our rogue banker?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,空管局证实阿方索·朗四天前从赫瓦诺拉飞往杜勒斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}TSA confirms Alfonso Lang flew from Hewanorra to Dulles four days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他有记录么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Did he have a sheet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有许多洗钱的指控\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}A lot of raps for money laundering,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但他都驳回了  否则他会被列入禁飞名单\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}all of which he's beaten, otherwise he'd be on the no-fly list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你查到他的具体位置了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You got a 411 on his location?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,只是在国际刑警组织的线人告诉我他会见了客户\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Just a contact at Interpol telling me he meets with clients
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在区内经常搞税务诈骗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}in the district regularly to set up tax scams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我会联系大使馆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I'll contact the embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:07:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,看看他是否在他们的观察名单上还触犯了底线\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}See if he's on one of their watch lists and tripped a wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,圣卢西亚是英国的保护国\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}St. Lucia's a British protectorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  圣卢西亚是一个主权国家  英联邦的一部分\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Actually, St. Lucia's a sovereign nation. Part of the Commonwealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,干得好  查尔斯  你应该上推理小节目了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Well done, Charles. You should go on Jeopardy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And you should...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也去那里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Go on it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  肯德拉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Hey, Kendra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以  我会去的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Of course, I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,白宫顾问有个紧急事件需要帮助\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}White House Counsel needs help with an urgent matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题  我一找到线索就联系你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}No problem. I'll call you as soon as I find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  表现好点  孩子们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}All right. Play nice, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不知道是谁送的这封信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}No, I don't know who sent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但一字一句都是对的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}But every word's true. I'm innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们重审了你的档案\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}We reviewed your file.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你在2001年被指控谋杀了一位名叫卡尔·马利的缉毒局特工\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You were convicted of murdering a DEA agent named Carl Marley in 2001.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,一剂氯胺酮致死\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}A ketamine sting gone bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,检察官说服陪审团\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}The prosecutor convinced the jury
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,相信你的药店有财务危机\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}that your pharmacy was in financial trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就说我在黑市上卖K粉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And that I was selling ketamine on the black market
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我连马路都不乱穿\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}when I'd never even jaywalked?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他的尸体就在你店附近的一个公园被发现\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}His body was found in a park near your store.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,被一把没有登记过的枪射在脸上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Shot in the face with a gun that was never located.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你储藏室的地板上找到了他的血迹\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Traces of his blood were found on your storage room floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那屋子每天有20个人进进出出  任何人都有可能带进来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Twenty people were in that room every day. Anyone could've tracked it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你的庭审律师呢  我们能和他谈谈吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}What about your trial lawyer? Can we talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不能了  他三年前就死了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}No. He died three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他活着的时候也没啥用处\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}But he was pretty worthless when he was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,庭审之后你还剩多少钱\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}How much money did you have left after the trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,事实证明  刚够上诉的钱\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}As it turned out, just enough to appeal the sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,德恩先生  这个案子情况很特殊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Mr. Dern, this was a highly circumstantial case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你的律师不称职  我们会帮你调查这个案子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Your lawyer did a bad job. We're going to look into this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了  但是我想我已经没有上诉的机会了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}That's great. But I believe I've exhausted my appeals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是上诉  这是减刑\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It wouldn't be an appeal. It would be a commutation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是总统批准的  我无话可说\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}If the president were to grant that, I wouldn't have words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我期待正义太久了  从来都没等到\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}But I've been waiting for justice a long time, and it's never come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,希望是个可怕的东西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Hope is a dangerous thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想像一个懦夫一样祈祷永远不会来的缓刑\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I don't wanna die a coward praying for a reprieve that's never coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我想给孩子们留的榜样\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}That's not a legacy I want for my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那就别祈祷  做好准备\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Then don't pray. Prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的交给我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And let us do our thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,钱德勒·德恩有两个硕士学位\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Chandler Dern has two master's degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一个律师  甚至是一个三脚猫律师\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Does it make sense to you that a lawyer, even a crooked one,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,都能说服他不上诉  这说得通吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}could convince him that it was a good idea not to appeal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一点也说不通\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Not even a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他有一个儿子在盖瑟斯堡  我们看看他有什么要说的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He has a son in Gaithersburg. Let's see what he has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.47,0:09:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你与我们交谈\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Thanks for talking to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴你们在调查我父亲的判决\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I'm thrilled that you're looking into my father's sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,总统有可能介入吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Is there a chance the president might step in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.94,0:09:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这取决于我们的调查\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It depends on our investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我有什么能帮的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}How can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得你父亲可能有没跟我们坦白的吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Is there a reason your father wouldn't be forthcoming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他跟你们说什么了  - 这不是关于他告诉我们什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- What did he tell you? - It's not what he told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们让你告诉我们什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It's what we're asking you to tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很有意思  你对你父亲很上心\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It's interesting. You're devoted to your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,监狱的探访日志显示你每周去那里两次\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Visitor logs at the prison say you're there twice a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但你的妹妹  特雷西  已经16年没去看他了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}But your younger sister, Tracy, hasn't been to see him in 16 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很好奇为什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}We're wondering why.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈在我6岁的时候去世了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}My mom died when I was six.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲被抓走的时候我17岁\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I was 17 when they took him away, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我挺过来了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I got through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我还开了家汽修公司\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I set up an auto repair business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,特雷西就没有那么幸运了  但我父亲  他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Tracy, she wasn't so lucky. But my dad, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他告诉我们要把家庭放在第一位  我不想谈论特雷西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He told us to always put family first. I'm not talking about Tracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有时间游戏了  你父亲现在命悬一线\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}We don't have time for games. Your father's life is on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我妹妹  她经常吸毒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}My sister, she's always had problems with drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她经常和一些坏人一起闲逛\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}She used to hang out with some bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我父亲害怕他的调查会牵连到她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I think that my father was afraid his investigation would implicate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人在你父亲的审判中作为辩护出现了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Were those people used as a defense in your father's trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  我父亲不让\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}No. My dad wouldn't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们在哪能找到你妹妹  - 不能\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Where can we find your sister? -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他知道我告诉你们这些  他就不认我了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}If he knew I told you any of this, he would disown me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克  你父亲就要被判处死刑了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Frank, your father is about to be put to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为认不认你现在不是首要问题\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I don't think disowning you is the issue here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫很帅  戈夫夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Your husband was very handsome, Mrs. Goff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔是我的全部\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Daniel was my everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,总统被你的信感动了  你能再多告诉我们点吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}The president was moved by your letter. Could you tell us more?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔在2013年被派往坎大哈  对战伊斯兰国\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Daniel was sent to Kandahar in 2013 to battle ISIL.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,国际维和部队的一部分\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Part of the international peacekeeping force.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  首批美国伤亡人员之一\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yes. One of the first American casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:11:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在他的葬礼上  他的一个士兵  曼凯维奇下士告诉我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}At his funeral, one of his soldiers, Corporal Mankiewicz, told me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔单枪匹马地把叛乱分子挡在海湾  直到救援到达\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Daniel single-handedly kept the insurgents at bay until help could arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他阻止他们越过美国的阵地\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He stopped them from overrunning the American position.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-  这听起来非常英勇  - 我也这么认为\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- That sounds like conspicuous bravery. -I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我写给他的上司  陆军上校\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}But I wrote his CO, Colonel Baines...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有理我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And he ignored me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,过去四年  我写了12封信  他一封都没回\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Twelve letters over the past four years, and he didn't answer one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔曾经告诉我特种部队就像家人一样\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Daniel once told me Special Forces was like family,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这不是对待家人的方式\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}but this is not how you treat family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的儿子  小丹尼  现在7岁了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Our son, Danny Junior, is seven now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,问起他的爸爸\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Asking about his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我想告诉他  他的父亲是一名战争英雄\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I would like to tell him his dad was a war hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不是死在几万公里之外的某个陌生人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}not just some stranger who died 10,000 miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们代表总统  向您承诺会调查这件事情\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}On behalf of the president, we promise to look into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,戈夫中士的部队在坎大哈遭到伏击\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Sergeant Goff's unit was ambushed in Kandahar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,迫击炮  流弹  机枪  他们被困了几个小时\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Mortars. RPGs. Machine guns. They were pinned down for hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,伤亡惨重\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Took a lot of casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来能活下来的都应该得块奖章\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It sounds you deserve a medal for even coming through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我同意  但戈夫不在那里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I agree. But Goff wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Where was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他在喀布尔德瓦扎区进行侦察\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He was doing recon in the Kabul Dwarza district.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他离开了  就是在这  简易爆炸装置取走了他的性命\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It's a click away, that's where the IED took him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你向戈夫中士的遗孀解释这个问题了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Did you explain this to Sergeant Goff's widow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好多次了  但她还是坚持写信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Repeatedly. But she kept writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是第一个想要自己的丈夫被认可的遗孀\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}She is not the first widow that wants recognition for her husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但事实就是事实\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}but facts are facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,经历过几次之后  我就不再回应了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}After some time, I had to stop responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还有其他目击者吗  - 只有曼凯维奇下士\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Were there any other witnesses? - Just Corporal Mankiewicz.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他给了她奖章的念头\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He put the idea of a medal in her ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 曼凯维奇现在在哪  - 他死了  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- So where's Mankiewicz now? - He's dead, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他服役期满一年后自杀了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He committed suicide a year after leaving the service.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,根据这些  他是唯一潜在的目击者了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}According to this, he was the only potential witness left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我想是这样的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I guess that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 迈克  你想补充点什么吗  - 这不合规矩  长官\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Mike, you wanna add something? - It's not appropriate, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果是我问你呢  - 只是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- It is if I'm asking. - It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那是戈夫的部队\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}That was Goff's unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:13:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们正在和敌人对峙的话\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It doesn't make sense he'd be a click away from his men
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.12,0:13:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有理由扔下自己的部队离开\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}if they were expecting hostiles, which they would've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得陆军上校搞错了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You think Colonel Baines is mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是我的观点  长官\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}In my opinion, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克在特种部队服役了六年\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Mike served six years, Special Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他认为没有要补充的  就没有要补充的了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}If he doesn't think something's adding up, something's not adding up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 继续挖掘  - 是的长官\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Dig deeper. -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 艾米莉  我能耽误一会儿吗  - 当然可以  长官\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Emily, can I borrow you? -Of course, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他们这周一直在鼓吹这个\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}They've been banging the drum on this all week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,媒体注意到了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}The media's picked it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是弗斯特试图诱使亚历克斯现在作证的原因\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}That's why Foerstel's trying to induce Alex to testify now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道热度在上升\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He knows the heat's turning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他正试图利用时机优势\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He's trying to take advantage of the timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天从他办公室得到一个消息\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I got a message from his office today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他有辛辛那提地区警方虐待调查的最新情况\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He has an update on the Cincinnati area police abuse investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么  这已经休眠好几个月了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Why? That's been dormant for months.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道  时机太奇怪了  - 不  一点也不奇怪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- I know. The timing's odd. - No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他想谈谈我妻子传唤的记录\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He wants to talk off the record about my wife's subpoena.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么他联系你而不是肯德拉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}That's why he contacted you instead of Kendra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要我跟他见见吗  - 是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Do you want me to take the meeting? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他一谈到伊卡洛斯  你就赶紧离开\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}The second he talks about Icarus, walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望这个办公室有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I don't want this office to have the slightest appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,任何妨碍调查的痕迹\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}of trying to obstruct this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明白  - 谢谢你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Understood. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:14:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 主管先生  - 谢谢你见我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Mr. Director. - Thanks for meeting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你有辛辛那提调查的最新情况\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You have an update on the Cincinnati investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我的意见是可能存在不法行为\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yes. My considered opinion is there may have been wrongdoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,严重的不法行为\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Serious wrongdoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的观点是  到现在为止  现有的事实并不能支持这一结论\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And our opinion is that the facts to date don't remotely support that conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这是临时意见  这也是为什么调查还要继续下去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It's provisional opinion, which is why an investigation has to continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一个什么样的客观观察者\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Despite the fact you're chasing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,会不管你正在追查的事实而含沙射影\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}what any objective observer would describe as innuendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,狂野的阴谋论\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Wild conspiracy theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的调查都会追踪事实  直到披露事情的真相\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}All investigations chase those things until they disclose the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,或者什么也证明不了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Or turn up nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,同时  对你正在调查的人也会造成损害\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Meanwhile, damage is done to those you're investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果调查对象是无辜的  他们不会有任何损害\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}If the subjects of this investigation are innocent, there won't be any damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道这不是事实\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}We both know that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,声誉可能受到伤害  机构会受到侵蚀\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Reputations can be harmed. Institutions eroded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我要关心的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}That's not my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你想让我告诉总统的吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Is that what you want me to tell the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他辛辛那提不是个人的  这是专业\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Tell him Cincinnati is not personal. It's professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我有责任让美国人民跟沿着这条道路走到最后\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And I owe a duty to the American people to follow this to the end of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,弗斯特想强调他不会屈服\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Foerstel wanted to underscore he wouldn't stand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没想到他会这样  - 这就是为什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Didn't think he would. - And here's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,媒体报道了伊卡洛斯调查\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}The media's covering the Icarus investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他把自己的职业声誉赌在结果上了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He's staking his professional credibility on the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是一名职业公务员  这不成问题\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Not a problem if you're a career civil servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是他是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Which he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不会长远的  我有预感  长官\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Not for long. I played a hunch, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我在奥尔巴尼找到了他的消息来源  事实证明\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I reached out to a source in Albany, where he's from, and it turns out,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就在伊卡洛斯调查开始的时候\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}he formed an exploratory committee for a 2018 New York Senate run,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他组建了一个2018年纽约参议院的探索委员会\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}right when the Icarus investigation began.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他也有一个秘密的政治行动委员会\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He has a secret PAC in the works, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经筹集了50万美元\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}They've already raised half a million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他正在调查案子的背景\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He's doing it on the back of the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们知道你注重过程\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}We know you respect process,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们建议你指定一个特别检察官来调查\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}so we're recommending you appoint a special prosecutor to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一位特别检察官吗  - 是的 先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}-A special prosecutor? -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这并不会结束伊卡洛斯一案的调查\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It doesn't end the Icarus investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,只是单纯的把弗斯特剔出去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It simply removes Foerstel from the equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,鉴于他可能居心叵测\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Which is in the best interest of the White House
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.37,0:15:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这样是对白宫最好的方式\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}since he may have ulterior motives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有抱负并不是居心叵测\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Ambition is not an ulterior motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是在这里生存的必备副产品罢了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It's a by-product of the work that gets done in this town
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没人可以避免\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}and no one's immune.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 作为总统我也一样  - 先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}-Present company included. -Sir--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,关于特别检察官一事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}With regards to a special prosecutor,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,以往的经验说明事情会一发不可收拾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}history tells me that they're runaway trains.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,调查一个接一个  如此往复\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}One investigation turns into another, etcetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,太过冒险了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Way too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是两害取其轻  我们可以承担这个风险\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It's the lesser of two evils. A risk we can manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米莉  我明白\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Emily, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我会仔细考虑的  谢谢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I'll take it under advisement. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您  总统先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,三信日  是吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Hey, so three-letter day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,对  三信日\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yeah. Three-letter day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  我能跟你说几句话吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Wait, hang on. Um, can I talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Uh, I've got a thing I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我也有事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Look, um, I have a thing, too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如履薄冰\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It's called walking on eggshells,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我过去几天的状态\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}which is what I feel like I've been doing the last few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好奇我帮我哥哥隐藏毒品被抓的事情\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I'm wondering if you told the president that I got arrested
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉总统了没有  这对我很重要\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}for covering up my brother's drugs, and what that means for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我也是很注重就业保障的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Because I'm also obsessed with this thing called job security.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,事态在升级\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It's an evolving situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,升级  知道了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}"Evolving." Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是一个问题\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}That's also a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.94,0:16:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,趣味小知识  蜂群一次培养出很多蜂后\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Interesting fact. A colony rears several queens at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,第一只受孕排卵的蜂后会在蜂巢内把其他蜂后都扎死\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}The first queen that hatches stings the others to death in their cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果两只同时排卵  他们会以死决胜负\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}If two emerge at once, they fight until one is killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像选举一样\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It's just like an elections.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来不是要当养蜂人的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I didn't set out to be an apiarist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始只是爱好  不知不觉  我有了三个蜂巢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It began as a hobby, and before I knew it, I had three colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那他们的维护肯定要花不少时间\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Their upkeep must take a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是  但我现在每月能从我的蜂巢中获利价值4000美元的蜂蜜\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yes. But I now harvest $4,000 a month worth of honey from my hives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害  我们需要怎么帮你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}That's excellent. So, how can we help?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,埃迪相信联邦航空局正在杀掉我们的蜜蜂\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Eddie thinks the FAA is killing our bees.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  如何杀掉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Really? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那个监控空中航线的雷达设施\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}That new Air Route Surveillance Radar facility,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大约就是在我的蜜蜂们灭绝的时候开始启用的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}it opened around the time of the die-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,蜜蜂通过磁场找寻方向\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Bees navigate using magnetic fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,雷达会变成一种干扰\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I think the radar is disrupting that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是飞的撞树上了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Are they flying into trees?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不  赛斯  他们是昆虫  不是弱智\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}No, Seth. They're insects, not imbeciles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他们使用太阳罗盘来导航\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}They use a solar compass to navigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦被干扰  相当于破坏了他们的空间记忆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Disrupt that, you compromise their spatial memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,无法找到食物\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}They can't find their food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你看来是个蜂类专家啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You must be a fellow melittologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,稍有涉猎  你跟航路监控雷达那边谈过了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I dabble. So you've spoken with the ARSR?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,谈过了  我告诉他们我三个蜂群中的两个都被彻底消灭了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yes. I told them two of my three colonies had been completely wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们无视我  所以我才给总统写了信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}But they ignored me. That's why I wrote the president a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 埃迪非常有主动性  - 白宫亦如此\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}-Eddie's very proactive. -So is the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不想给你们添麻烦的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Oh, we didn't mean to put you to all this trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.06,0:18:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不会  有麻烦的是联邦航空局\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Oh, no. The trouble will be the FAA's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.02,0:18:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,让东方蜜蜂原地待命  救援在路上了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Tell  Apis cerana  to stand by. Help's on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,再联络\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Uh, we'll be in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣的小知识\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Interesting fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 蜜蜂从不睡觉的  - 关我什么事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}-Bees never sleep. -I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是唯一为人类制造食物的昆虫\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}They're the only insect that produces food for humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我有什么关系吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I still don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你被蛰过  不是吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Oh, you've been stung, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,斯莱特先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Hey, Ms. Slater.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我是赛斯·怀特  这位是里奥·布恩  感谢您的到来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Seth Wright. This is Lyor Boone. Thank you so much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,对于总统对航天事业的兴趣  我局非常激动\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}On behalf of the FAA, we're thrilled the president has an interest in aviation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那倒没有  他只是对蜜蜂感兴趣而已\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Oh, he doesn't. His interest is in bees.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 天  不会又是那个叫埃迪的吧  - 你记得他吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}-Oh, God. Not that Eddie guy again. -You remember him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,作为航线检测雷达部的负责人  我差点要申请一个针对他的限制令\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}As the administrator of the ARSR, I have a hard time forgetting someone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这种人我怎么可能会忘记\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I nearly got a restraining order against.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 信件  电话  纠察队  - 你全部当做没看见\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}-The letters. The calls. The pickets. -All of which you ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}No, we didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们试图达成友好一致的解决办法  但问题自己解决掉了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}We tried to reach an amicable settlement, but the problem resolved itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我以为是这样的额\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Or I thought it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁告诉你的  - 海伦·艾德森\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}-Who told you that? -Helen Adamson.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他妻子啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}His wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是她  钱德勒的女儿\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}That's her. Chandler's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,德恩夫人  我也是汉娜  联邦调查局的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Ms. Dern? I'm Hannah Wells. FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是肯德拉·戴恩斯  白宫顾问\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}This is Kendra Daynes. The White House Counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我给你留了留言  - 我没什么好说的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}-I've left you messages. -I've nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是关于你父亲的  你还记得他  不是吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It's about your dad. You remember him, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,温特黑文  你在那里呆了蛮久啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Winter Haven? You spend a lot of time there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦不要打扰我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Please leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是你就你父亲的事情给我们写信得嘛  - 不是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}-Did you write to us about your Dad? -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,崔西  我们是为白宫工作的  如果你父亲真的清白  我们可以救他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Tracy We work for the White House. If your Dad is innocent, we can save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你知道任何可以帮助我们证明\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}If you know something that can help us prove--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  请让我走吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I don't. Now please, let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她都不敢直视我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}She couldn't even look us in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是于心有愧  我们分析一下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Could be a guilty conscience. but let's play it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她年轻的时候吸过毒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}She's a strung-out teen back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,莫名其妙掺和到克他命交易里  中间人死了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}somehow got mixed up in the ketamine buy. The agent's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他父亲替她顶了罪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Her dad takes the fall for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就在他父亲临死前  她屈服了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}When he's looking at his last meal, she finally caves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,写了信来挽救父亲的生命\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Writes a letter to save his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看她有没有前科记录  贩毒定罪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I'll see if she has a rap sheet, prior drug convictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  我得去和代理瑞内特见面讨论第一夫人的案子了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Okay. I have to meet Agent Rennett about the First Lady's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一小时之后白宫见吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}See you in the White House in an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一有消息我就通知你  - 好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}-I'll call as soon as I hear something. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,来了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你今天挺神秘啊 - 对  三信日嘛\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}-You've been scarce. -Yeah, it's three-letter day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是某种邮政节日吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Is that some sort of postal holiday?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不是  银行家那里查到了什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}No, it's... What do we have on the banker?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,朗先生有双重国籍\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Our Mr. Lang has dual citizenship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,同时持有圣卢西亚和英国护照\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}St. Lucia and the UK. Multiple passports.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他是使用圣卢西亚护照落地美国的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He landed here using his St. Lucia passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,几天前用英国护照去了加拿大\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Used his British one to pass into Canada a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,鉴于他对双重身份的滥用  我们无法及时抓到他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He's exploiting multiple identities so we can't catch him in real time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真是赶在银行业立法者前头的好方法\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Good way to stay one step ahead of the banking regulators.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们的系统更新出他的信息  他可能都跑到加德满都去了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}By the time our systems update, he could be in Kathmandu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须找到他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}We have to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他是避免第一夫人不被FBI询问的最后希望了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He's the First Lady's last hope to avoid the FBI inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:20:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,阿方索·朗在乔治城有所公寓\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Alfonso Lang has a condo in Georgetown
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他是从一家叫做蒙特拉特联盟的寡头控股公司那里租的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}he leases through a closely held corporation called Montserrat Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.10,0:21:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我把地址发给你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I'm texting you the address.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都无法确认他在不在美国\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}We don't know that he's in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以确认  我查到了公司信用卡一个半小时以前的消费记录\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I do. I can trace a purchase to a company credit card 90 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在杜邦的一家按摩妓院  - 谢了  查克\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}-A massage parlor in Dupont. -Thanks, Chuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,朗在本地  查克马上把具体信息发给我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Lang's local. Chuck is texting us the deets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.53,0:21:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们能让朗坦白  他是为埃劳德办事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}If we can get Lang to confess that he was working at Lloyd's behest
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,制造了第一夫人从伊卡洛斯那里受贿的假象\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}to make it look like the First Lady was getting a payola from Icarus,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就可以还她清白\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}we can clear her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.58,0:21:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我去上个厕所  等下见\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Great. I'm gonna hit the loo. I'll see you in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你记得部分车牌吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You got a partial plate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:21:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,前三个字母  查克在查了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}First three letters. Chuck's running it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:22:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是宝贵的一课啊  - 什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}-There's a lesson here. -What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你不应该单挑银行家\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You shouldn't beat up bankers without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是想要陷害第一夫人的银行家\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Especially bankers who want to frame the First Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得是你的话躲得开那辆车吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You think you could've gotten out of the way of that car?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.62,0:22:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不  但我会在他上车前就打到他的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Nope. I would've shot the guy before he got in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,朗先生  汉娜·威尔斯  联邦调查局的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Mr. Lang? Hannah Wells. FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,电视开着呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}TV's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.51,0:22:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定不是某人在求救吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You sure that's not someone calling for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.26,0:22:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,紧急情况  不需要搜捕令\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Exigent circumstances. No need for a warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.72,0:22:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你确实在这里呆了蛮久\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You really have been here too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但不如我久\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I've been here longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.27,0:22:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.82,0:22:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,朗先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Mr. Lang?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.53,0:22:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他刚走\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}We just missed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.04,0:22:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有人给他报信了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Someone tipped him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.37,0:22:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,贝恩斯上校  我们还有一些关于坎大哈的问题\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Colonel Baines, we have more questions about Kandahar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.96,0:22:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是戈夫中士打仗时\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Those are the GPS coordinates of Sergeant Goff's phone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,被杀位置所显示的手机GPS坐标\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}during the battle in which he was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:22:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这些坐标有趣在哪里吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You know what's interesting about these coordinates?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.13,0:23:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把戈夫中士放在战场中央\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}They put Sergeant Goff in the middle of the battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.47,0:23:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,距离侦查地点很近\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}not a click away doing recon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解的信息就是这样的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}That's the information I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.97,0:23:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那我现在来给你看看我们了解的信息\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Let me show you the information we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一份离婚申请  你的离婚申请\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}This is a divorce filing. Your divorce filing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.35,0:23:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,离婚理由写的是通奸\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And it lists adultery as the grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你妻子和戈夫中士的婚外情\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}An affair your wife had with Sergeant Goff.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.98,0:23:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,提交有误材料是对军事法庭的藐视\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Filing a false report is a court-martial offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,开除军籍  坐牢服刑  这些都不用我说了吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Dishonorable discharge. Prison time. I don't need to tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.53,0:23:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不用\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.15,0:23:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你要对戈夫中士的行为重新陈述\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}So you will amend your statement of Sergeant Goff's conduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.53,0:23:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你要推荐他为国牺牲值得获得荣誉勋章\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And you'll recommend that he be posthumously awarded the Medal of Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.12,0:23:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我会的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.00,0:23:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.92,0:23:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会遗漏任何一个\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And I won't leave out any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.09,0:23:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅是因为他背叛了我的信任\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Not how he betrayed my trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.34,0:23:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,引诱我的妻子  毁了我的婚姻  或是种种行为\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Or seduced my wife. Or ruined my marriage, or any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他的遗孀可以把我的证词挂在他的荣誉勋章旁\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And his widow can frame my statement right next to his Medal of Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.31,0:23:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.44,0:23:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说来你们不同意问候戈夫军士\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}So both of you disagree with regards to Sergeant Goff?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.65,0:24:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我们一致认为他的英勇应该被认可\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yes. We both agree he should be recognized for his valor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.07,0:24:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但是勋章是给生者的  并非亡者  勋章慰藉人心\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}But medals are for the living, not the dead. They provide comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.70,0:24:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们把勋章颁给戈夫军士的话\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}If we award this medal to Sergeant Goff,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.78,0:24:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他的妻子也将知道他的不忠\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}his wife will also learn about his infidelity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.12,0:24:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不同意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And I disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.79,0:24:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这些调查的关注点太局限  都靠战场上的事实来决定\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}These inquiries have a narrow focus, to determine the facts on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.08,0:24:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哪些是值得赞扬的功勋\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Which deserve commendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.00,0:24:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  一旦你把外来人员的情况考虑进来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yes. Once you factor extraneous personal circumstances into the mix--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.25,0:24:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,勋章就是关于外来人员情况的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}The medal is about extraneous personal circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.42,0:24:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那它对于近亲属又将意味着什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}What it will mean to the next of kin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.80,0:24:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能给予近亲属最好的礼物便是真相\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}The greatest gift we can give the next of kin is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.43,0:24:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我想见见戈夫夫人和她的儿子  就在总统办公室这里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I would like to meet with Mrs. Goff and her son, here in the Oval Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.35,0:24:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.44,0:24:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以提一下另一件事吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}May I address another matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.57,0:24:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可以  说吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Sure, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.32,0:24:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我来这是拥护透明制度的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I'm here championing for transparency.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.61,0:24:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我愧于承认我没能像您一样坦率透明\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I'm ashamed to admit I haven't been as transparent with you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.28,0:24:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我本该处理好个人问题的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}as I should have been regarding a personnel issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.28,0:24:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,请继续\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.45,0:24:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,几年前  赛斯被捕控告\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}A few days ago, Seth was arrested and charged--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.79,0:24:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这件事的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I already know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.21,0:25:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,您知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.21,0:25:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哥伦比亚地区检察官是我的朋友  我们一起打牌\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}The District of Columbia DA is a friend. We play cards together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.47,0:25:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我一从喀布尔回来他就告诉我了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He told me as soon as I got back from Kabul.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.97,0:25:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉我没及时讨论这个问题\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I'm sorry we didn't have this conversation sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.43,0:25:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.60,0:25:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,重点是  我们正待面临\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}The point is, we're having it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.31,0:25:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我也知道白宫是个大家庭\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I know that the White House is like a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.31,0:25:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我想象不到这有时对你来说有多难\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I can't imagine how difficult it is for you sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.98,0:25:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,与大家在同一个战壕里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}in the trenches with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.23,0:25:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.19,0:25:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但你为我效力\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}But you work for me
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.73,0:25:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我在暗处是无法工作的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}and I can't do my job when I'm kept in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.45,0:25:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我依靠你就这类问题上进尽忠言\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I rely on you to counsel me through these kinds of matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.03,0:25:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.74,0:25:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,说到这里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Having said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.88,0:25:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,处理赛斯这件事你有什么想法\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}What do you think I should do about Seth?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.22,0:25:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.30,0:25:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.31,0:25:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,看他们  多么单纯  又脆弱\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Look at them. So innocent. So vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.56,0:26:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,它们只是蜜蜂  里奥\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}They're bees, Lyor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.94,0:26:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  里奥  等一下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Wait, Lyor, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.40,0:26:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,控诉  海伦阿达姆松  正义必须被维护\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}J'accuse,  Helen Adamson. Justice must be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.78,0:26:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  等等  里奥  放松点\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Wait, wait. Lyor, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.15,0:26:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我很放松\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I am relaxed.
