Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.96,0:30:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真想杀了她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Oh, speaking of someone I wanna kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.38,0:30:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你胆敢提她的名字\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Don't you dare mention her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.88,0:30:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我真该嫁给兰斯波顿逊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I should have married Lance Burtleson.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.39,0:30:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,兰斯  你倒是嫁啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Lance? Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.81,0:30:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有人想要撞倒你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Someone tried to run you down?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.81,0:30:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是职业风险  我还好 和我说说话\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It's an occupational hazard. I'm fine. Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.02,0:30:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我在系统中查了查特蕾西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I checked Tracy in the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.69,0:30:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,无记录  不过我从另一个德恩身上找到了线索\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}No record. But I got a hit from another Dern.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.98,0:30:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她的兄弟  弗兰克  -什么罪名\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Her brother, Frank. -What's his collar for?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.78,0:31:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,2001年 毒品罪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Drug conviction in 2001.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.65,0:31:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在他父亲犯罪的六个月后\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Six months after his dad's conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.03,0:31:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不良行为罪和持有麻醉品罪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Misdemeanor and possession of ketamine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.74,0:31:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是当年一种稀有的致幻药\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Which was a rare designer drug back in 2001.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.87,0:31:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有可能钱德勒德恩是在包庇什么人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Meaning if Chandler Dern was covering for someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.08,0:31:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不是他女儿\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}it wasn't his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.00,0:31:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 互相传个话  - 好的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}-Keep each other posted. -Deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.21,0:31:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,总统要特赦我吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Is the president going to pardon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.30,0:31:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你说真话\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Not unless you tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.71,0:31:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了16年真话  我是清白的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I've been telling the truth for 16 years. I'm innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.84,0:31:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.05,0:31:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我还相信你知道谁是有罪的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And I also believe you know who's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.56,0:31:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这是弗兰克的逮捕笔录\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}This is Frank's arrest record.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.64,0:31:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这之间有什么关系吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}What does that have to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.89,0:31:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道那天晚上发生了什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}We both know what happened that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.02,0:31:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你的儿子想买麻醉剂  但事情出差错了  他就杀了卡尔·马利\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Your son tried to buy ketamine. It went wrong. He killed Carl Marley.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.19,0:31:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是真的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.40,0:31:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了替罪羊  让你的女儿保密\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You took the fall. And made your daughter keep the secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.70,0:31:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事让她崩溃\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And it destroyed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.49,0:31:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但她还是遵你所言\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}But she kept faith with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.66,0:31:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,直到她再也忍不下去  因为她不想眼看着她父亲送命\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Until she couldn't anymore because she didn't wanna watch her father die.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.16,0:31:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你认为我会放弃我的儿子  你肯定不曾有过孩子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}If you think I'm gonna give up my son, you must not have children.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.83,0:31:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你已被宣判为有罪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You've been tried and convicted for this crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.25,0:32:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没有检察官会因此而指控弗兰克\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}No prosecutor on Earth will try to charge Frank for this now,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.13,0:32:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,更不会说服陪审团判他有罪了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}let alone try to convince a jury to convict him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.13,0:32:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但人们会知道的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}But the world will know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.68,0:32:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,邓恩先生  如果你想让总统赦免你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Mr. Dern, if you want the president to pardon you,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.39,0:32:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他需要从你嘴里听到真相\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}he needs to hear the truth from your lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.39,0:32:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我最后悔的就是对特蕾西造成的伤害\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I regret the damage done to Tracy more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.19,0:32:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我的死能让她再次圆满  那我死而无憾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And I would gladly die if it would make her whole again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.03,0:32:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但我现在帮不了她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}But I can't help her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.24,0:32:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我能救弗兰克\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I can help Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.82,0:32:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他还有大好人生  我愿意牺牲自己来保住他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He has a life. And I will sacrifice mine so that he can keep his.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.99,0:32:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,警卫\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.91,0:32:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.84,0:32:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.46,0:32:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就一小会儿\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}This will just take a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.92,0:32:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我已决定向总统提出辞呈\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I've decided to offer the president my resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.84,0:32:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.18,0:32:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,前两天我一直躲在这里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I've been skulking around here the last two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.76,0:32:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他清楚我被捕了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I know he knows I've been arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.31,0:32:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我能从他看我的眼神里看出来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I can see it in the way he looks at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.31,0:32:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,从他说话语气里听出来  他让我去查看蜜蜂\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I can hear it in his tone. He put me on bee patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.02,0:32:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他向来关注蜜蜂\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He cares about bees.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.31,0:32:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,和里尔一起查看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Bee patrol with Lyor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.77,0:33:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.27,0:33:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我被弃如敝履  却不知该怎么办\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I'm in the doghouse. I don't know how to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.15,0:33:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想向他提交辞呈\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}So I figure I'll offer him my resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.28,0:33:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他同意了  那很好  不然的话\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}If he accepts, I know I'm good. If not--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.24,0:33:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他不会同意的  - 你怎么知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- He won't accept it. - How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.37,0:33:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我建议他辞掉你  他拒绝了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Because I told him to fire you. And he declined.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.79,0:33:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不得不客观一些  - 我明白\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- I had to be objective. - No, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.05,0:33:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,客观来讲我认为你的行为是不忠诚的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}An objective Emily would view your behavior as disloyal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.63,0:33:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你向一个绝不能妥协的人做出了妥协\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You compromised the one person you can't compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.39,0:33:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 而且是出于自愿  - 我明白\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- And you did it willingly. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.06,0:33:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,并且你向我做出了让步\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And you compromised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.44,0:33:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,事情发生后  我从各个角度去看待这件事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And I've looked at this every which way since it's gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.28,0:33:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,重新考虑了每一个选项\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I've reconsidered every option.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.32,0:33:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的答案\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And here's where I come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.99,0:33:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,重来一次也一样\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I would do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.33,0:33:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因为迈克尔是我的兄弟  我要保护我的家人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Because Michael's my brother and I protect my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.66,0:33:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.67,0:34:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这正是他不解雇你的原因\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And that's exactly why he won't fire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.05,0:34:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你有一张免罪卡  你只是使用了而已\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You get one "get out of jail free" card and you just used it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.38,0:34:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,所以现在呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}So what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.43,0:34:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.31,0:34:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,向前看  别在自责了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Now go forth and sin no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.23,0:34:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.15,0:34:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,为了什么  努力让你被解雇吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}For what? Trying to get you fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.03,0:34:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,为了你一直在做正确的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}For always doing the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.45,0:34:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,应该做的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}The right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.79,0:34:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.83,0:34:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,有时似乎不可能再看清真相了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Sometimes it seems impossible to know what that is anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.75,0:34:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.00,0:34:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你的案件总结十分清楚表明邓恩先生包庇了他的儿子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Your case summary makes it perfectly clear that Mr. Dern covered for his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.14,0:34:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对他来说是努力保护自己的家人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}In his mind, trying to protect his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.22,0:35:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管方法有误  但罪不至死\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}However misguided, I don't think anyone deserves to die for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.02,0:35:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我同意  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I agree, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.27,0:35:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,然而事实上  有一位联邦探员死亡了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}But the fact remains there's a dead federal agent
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.65,0:35:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,凶手逍遥法外\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}whose murderer's walking the streets
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.27,0:35:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,因为邓恩选择妨碍司法公正\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}because Mr. Dern chose to obstruct justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.99,0:35:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他必须为此付出代价\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}And he has to pay for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.95,0:35:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但并不是性命\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}But not with his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.04,0:35:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你减缓了他的判决\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}So you're commuting his sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.37,0:35:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  但没有减轻定罪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yes, but not his conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.91,0:35:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,除非他说出真相  否则他会在监狱里度过余生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He'll spend his life in prison unless he tells the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.92,0:35:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.09,0:35:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,能帮我接通监狱吗  谢谢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Can you patch me through to the penitentiary? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.55,0:35:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,差点撞了你的车是一辆银色轿车\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}The car that nearly hit you was a silver sedan,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.43,0:35:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,马里兰州牌照  开头是SK1\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Maryland plates that start with SK1.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.01,0:35:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我把目标缩减到了19人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I narrowed it to 19 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.77,0:35:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你把这份名单和阿方索·朗交叉比对过吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Did you cross-reference this list for connections to Alfonso Lang?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.43,0:35:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,比对过了  没有发现\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yeah. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.39,0:35:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,圣卢西亚联邦银行呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}What about the Federal Bank of St. Lucia?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.52,0:35:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,也搜索过了  没有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Ran that search, too.  Nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.06,0:35:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我会进行深层搜索\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I'll run a deeper search.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.15,0:35:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这些人和伊卡洛斯跟劳埃德之间有没有哪怕是间接联系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Look for even tangential contacts between these people and Icarus, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.90,0:35:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,19辆车可不是个小数目\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Nineteen cars is a lot of cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.82,0:35:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,的确是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yeah. It's a lot of cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.03,0:35:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但想杀我的人肯定会确保\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}But the person who tried to kill me would wanna make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.37,0:36:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这辆车不会被追踪到他们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}that this car wasn't traced back to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.12,0:36:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这个名单的有趣之处在哪里吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You know what's interesting about this list?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.12,0:36:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一辆车三天前发生了事故\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}One of the cars on it was in an accident three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.30,0:36:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你去哪  - 我有预感\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Where are you going? - I got a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.13,0:36:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我是对的  我就能知道是谁想杀我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}If I'm right, I'll know who tried to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.01,0:36:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好伙计们  明天见\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}That's good work, boys. See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.52,0:36:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.02,0:36:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,威尔斯探员\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Agent Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.40,0:36:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你知道了你父亲的减刑\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I assume you heard about your father's commutation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.44,0:36:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了  谢谢你的努力\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I did. Thank you for all your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.77,0:36:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能减刑真是太好了  - 没错\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- It's been a great relief. - I'm sure it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.36,0:36:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,看着他为了你犯下的谋杀而死一定很糟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It would be terrible to watch him die for a murder you committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.49,0:36:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不知道你在说什么  - 别装了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- I don't know what you're talking about. - Drop the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.79,0:36:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你我都清楚你永远不会承认\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}We both know you're never going to answer for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.71,0:36:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但你总要负责的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}But you will answer for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.08,0:36:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你大错特错了  - 不 错的是你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}-You're making a big mistake. -No, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.21,0:36:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你试图用在你店里维修的车杀掉我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}When you used a car that your shop was repairing to try and kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.55,0:36:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们知道开车的是你  你的办公室经理看见你上车了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}We know you were driving the car. Your office manager saw you get into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.34,0:36:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她看错了  - 举起手来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- She's mistaken. - Put your hands up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.01,0:36:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,放在车上  立刻\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}On the car. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.30,0:37:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,救你父亲就意味着我会毁掉你的名声\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Saving your dad meant that I would ruin your reputation,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.93,0:37:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你试着阻止我  猜猜怎么着\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}so you tried to run me down. Guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.43,0:37:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然过了16年  但你最终还是要进监狱  混蛋\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}It's been 16 years, but you're finally going to jail, you son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.32,0:37:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,第一夫人来了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I have the First Lady for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.37,0:37:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  艾娃  我正要回去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Thank you, Ava. Hey. I was just heading up to the Residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.04,0:37:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这不能等  你一定要解雇约翰·弗斯特\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}This couldn't wait. You need to fire John Foerstel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.41,0:37:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么  - 因为他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Why? - Because he is using his office
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.71,0:37:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,以权谋私\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}to create headlines for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.21,0:37:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他为了潜在的政治利益而故意把水搅浑\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He's purposely muddying the waters for potential political gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.46,0:37:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他背叛了职务誓言  这就是原因\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He's betraying his oath of office, that is why.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.88,0:37:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 艾利克斯  事情没有那么简单  - 不  就是这么简单\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Alex, it's not that easy. - Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.63,0:37:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,帕特里克·劳埃德已经死了两个月\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Patrick Lloyd has been dead for two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.59,0:37:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还在被他纠缠不休\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}We are still being haunted by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.55,0:37:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,虚构的银行账户\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}The fabricated bank account.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.14,0:37:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不存在的伊卡洛斯的阴谋\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}The conspiracy with Icarus that doesn't even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.60,0:37:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这些都不是真的  - 我知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- None of this is real. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.98,0:37:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,当你能有所作为时\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Why are you letting us get dragged down by an investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.73,0:37:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么还要让我们被调查拖累\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}when you can do something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.32,0:37:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我的工作人员们想要我任命一名特别检察官\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}My staff wants me to appoint a special prosecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.36,0:37:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我解雇弗斯特\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You want me to fire Foerstel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.28,0:38:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们都错过了关键  - 什么关键\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- You're all missing the point. - What is the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.37,0:38:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈犯了联邦重罪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Your mother committed a federal crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.16,0:38:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,可能在三十年前\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Thirty years ago, maybe,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.37,0:38:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但她犯了罪  就会有后果\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}but she committed a crime. There are consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.29,0:38:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能为了配合我们自己就去改变规则\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I can't just change the rules because it suits us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.71,0:38:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰·弗斯特准备竞选参议院\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}John Foerstel is preparing to run for Senate.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.71,0:38:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他违反了规则\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He is not playing by the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.63,0:38:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  见鬼  他违规了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yes, he is, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.96,0:38:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,也许不是我们期望的方式  但他只是在做自己的工作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}He's doing his job, maybe not the way we want him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.34,0:38:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能因此就解雇他  如果我那么做了  我又成了什么人呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I can't fire him for that. If I did, who would I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.80,0:38:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的丈夫\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}My husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.44,0:38:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.11,0:38:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信你竟然那么说\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I can't believe you just said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.15,0:38:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你质疑我作为丈夫的的承诺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You're questioning my commitment as a husband
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.94,0:38:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为我在一切正确时\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}because I won't interfere in an investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.74,0:38:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不愿意干扰调查\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}where we've done absolutely nothing wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.82,0:38:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,艾利克斯  你是个杰出的律师  却是个糟糕的被告\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You're a hell of a lawyer, Alex, but you're a lousy defendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.51,0:39:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再来些酒吗  - 好的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- More wine? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.93,0:39:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.02,0:39:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 都喝完了吗  - 是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- Are we out? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.95,0:39:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,半夜还在努力工作吗  查克\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Burning the midnight oil, Chuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.74,0:39:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  听着  我查了朗的手机  发现了一些东西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yes, listen, I got something. I ran Lang's cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.08,0:39:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你是对的  有人在你去他的公寓前\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}You were right. Somebody called him right before you got to his condo.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.04,0:39:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 用刻录机电话给他打了电话  - 知道是谁吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}- From a burner. - Do we know who it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.96,0:39:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不清楚  但我用三角定位法找到了发出信号的手机基站\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}No. But I triangulated the signal based on the cell phone towers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.00,0:39:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在第四大道和H街交汇处  下午两点二十二分\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Call came from 4th and H, 2:22 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.80,0:39:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去下卫生间  到时见\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}I'm gonna hit the loo. I'll meet you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.30,0:39:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,汉娜  你还在吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Hannah. Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.93,0:39:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,还在  谢谢  查克  回头再说\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Yeah. Thanks, Chuck, I'll talk to you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.77,0:39:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来呢  你要去工作还是和我寻欢作乐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Hey, what's it gonna be? Work or pleasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.20,0:40:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,和你开心下吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Pleasure.
